oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Del Reeves at Latonia Racetrack (16116)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Reeves, Del; Sovine, Red; Morgan, George, 1925-1975; Sharpe, Sunday; Reno, Jack; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on light brown) announcing Del Reeves, Jimmy Dickens, Red Sovine, George Morgan, Sunday Sharpe, and Jack Reno at the Latonia Racetrack in Florence, Kentucky on April 27. Poster features metal photoplates of Del Reeves, Jimmy Dickens, Red Sovine, George Morgan, Sunday Sharpe, and Jack Reno. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/39929.
